<view class="page">
  <view class="hero">
    <view class="eyebrow">
      <text class="cn">国际学生跨境顺路带物匹配</text>
      <text class="en">Cross-border carry matching for international students</text>
    </view>
    <view class="title">Student Carry</view>
    <view class="subtitle">
      <text class="cn">为留学生提供发布需求、浏览行程、沟通协商和线下确认的一站式匹配体验。</text>
      <text class="en">A student marketplace for posting requests, browsing carry routes, negotiating details, and confirming offline exchanges.</text>
    </view>
    <view class="button-row">
      <button class="primary-button" bindtap="goPost">帮我带 / Request</button>
      <button class="secondary-button" bindtap="goCarry">顺路送 / Carry</button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="how-section">
    <view class="section-title no-margin">如何使用 / How it works</view>
    <view class="stack-stage">
      <view
        wx:for="{{displaySteps}}"
        wx:key="number"
        class="stack-card pos-{{item.position}}"
      >
        <view class="stack-head">
          <view>
            <view class="step-number">{{item.number}}</view>
            <view class="step-title">{{item.titleCn}}</view>
            <view class="step-en">{{item.titleEn}}</view>
          </view>
          <view class="step-icon">{{item.number}}</view>
        </view>
        <view class="step-body">{{item.bodyCn}}</view>
        <view class="step-body muted">{{item.bodyEn}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="dots">
      <view
        wx:for="{{steps}}"
        wx:key="number"
        data-index="{{index}}"
        bindtap="setStep"
        class="{{activeStep === index ? 'dot active-dot-mini' : 'dot'}}"
      ></view>
    </view>

    <view class="example-card">
      <view class="item-title">Shanghai → Paris</view>
      <view class="item-line">Item: Documents · Reward: €20</view>
      <view class="item-line">Status: Looking for carrier</view>
      <view class="item-note">示例：从上海到巴黎带一份文件，预算 €20，等待顺路学生接单。</view>
      <view class="item-note muted">Example: Carry documents from Shanghai to Paris with a €20 reward, waiting for a student carrier.</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="notice">
    <text class="cn">安全与隐私</text>
    <text class="cn">我们提供基础匹配与沟通服务。用户个人信息默认不会公开展示，平台鼓励通过可信方式完成线下交接与确认。</text>
    <text class="en">Safety & Privacy</text>
    <text class="en">We provide basic matching and communication tools for students. Personal information is not publicly displayed by default, and users are encouraged to complete exchanges through trusted offline verification.</text>
  </view>

  <view class="notice danger-notice">
    <text class="cn">平台规则</text>
    <text class="cn">仅支持合法、可正常携带的小件物品。用户需自行确认海关、航空及目的地相关规定，禁止违禁品、灰产代购及受限制物品。</text>
    <text class="en">Platform Guidelines</text>
    <text class="en">Only legal and carry-on eligible small items are supported. Users are responsible for checking customs and airline regulations. Prohibited or restricted items are not allowed.</text>
  </view>
</view>
